                                button-through flap closure, and two zippered security back pockets
                            </li>
                            <li class="details__list-number">
                                Bonus pocket inside the right front pocket is perfect for carrying a small cell phone or
                                pocket knife
                            </li>
                            <li class="details__list-number">Non-roll stretch waistband</li>
                            <li class="details__list-number">Sturdy tunnelbelt loops</li>
                            <li class="details__list-number">Durable double fabric seat</li>
                            <li class="details__list-number">Gusset crotch</li>
                            <li class="details__list-number">Double-stitched seams throughout</li>
                            <li class="details__list-number">
                                Bar tack stitching reinforces areas of stress to guarantee years of service
                            </li>
                            <li class="details__list-number">
